Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么边睡边笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我笑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.17,0:02:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副全世界都很幸福的表情笑眯眯的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了一个很好的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很久以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是一个非常幸福的梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是想要去的地方的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.43,spec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,100)\b1\fs22}闭园通知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.43,spec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(570,160}本托儿所决定闭园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.43,spec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(550,190}在此向大家致以真诚的歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.43,spec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,205}非常抱歉  另外  如有事需要联络
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.43,spec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,170}请联系园长冲浦清花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.43,spec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(485,280}艾草托儿所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.43,spec,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(465,310}冲浦清花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:03:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要收拾哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧  有这么多张
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我会继续加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  为了让这里焕然一新必须要丢掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要丢掉…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绑好的就放到玄关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些弄完后去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本不在还真有点辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他工作很忙吧  藤本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不着勉强自己加班打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  请让我加班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不需要赚钱了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想解雇我的话请直说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定闭园这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢  我希望你可以明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为现在这样挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为冲浦说的话而闭园
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终决定的是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  可以来托儿所看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生还有东西在留在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部丢掉也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙  去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我要迟一个小时再去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  听说你今天会晚来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情很快办完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛一脸郁闷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都被你搞得浑身不舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么  你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很疼  艾草托儿所闭园了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对清花老师来说是件好事  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没点自觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  真是的
Comment: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:33.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要去打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可今天是拆除托儿所的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少今天应该请假才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  隔壁的都出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微出去走走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:11:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  晚上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要摆着副臭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你也快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  东西都搬出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天都搬出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在马上动工也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个眼神凶恶的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  真不招人喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明受过人家照顾  真够冷漠的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本先生他…很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲浦先生拜托过我  还反复叮嘱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说一段时间内不能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上头的种种原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然都是些我们这样的小职员不明白的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么冲浦先生他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心  他会搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是冲浦先生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  因为今天就要说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就来看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有好好和妈妈说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大  可以开工了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  可以开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  很危险的离远点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事没商量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄琥大人好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家居然偷偷享用点心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞祥  给我安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓兔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿兔子当人质  和那家伙谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以为神会答应这笔交易吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少比什么都不做来的强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我们的现状来看  这不是那么简单的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银生说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你说得在理多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的轻重什么的  事后想怎么改都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的事你一点教训都没学到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  二位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想采取极端手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.18,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的是究竟谁  你要是不明白的话就让我来告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  神想让你学到的说不定就是「等待」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那的确是我不擅长的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦  我什么都不会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫五百袛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是接下来要和你同行的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  善后工作完成后就禁止进入了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你们也多保重  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然之前也曾觉得这里相当宽敞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过以这种方式看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  我有事拜托你  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮藤本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾草托儿所或许一直在束缚着藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束缚…束缚什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束缚着藤本一直扮演不断努力的藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也依赖起了藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能早点发觉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了  藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清和老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹风琴给我们听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能对他说「请为了自己做自己喜欢的事吧」就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  藤本先生他真的很努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以才更要告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为他是努力过头的藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小鸠  藤本就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪在他身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的职责  已经不是了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠姐  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂元  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照约定  我没有连络艾草托儿所的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我对管理员小姐说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说不想让你担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也在以他的方式顾虑你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好只是轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要过于勉强自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只手不能动很不方便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我能帮上忙的事请尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始在艾草托儿所遇见你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果是因为同情或好奇心的话就别来了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是认为我可怜的话  还是免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  藤本先…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:20:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个满月之前要收集完金平糖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  就按照契约决定你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做才能延长期限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得今后会怎样  应该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢  看他的行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他确实感觉到了自己的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有那场战斗  那个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.67,0:22:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了牵连  不然不至落得如此下场…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是我能办到的我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  等到四季再次交替…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一个季节也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.36,0:22:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------NEXT-------------------
